ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
PrecisAppointment of JEAN-PHILIPPE BRUNET of Québec, Quebec, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Jean-Marc Dufour, whose term has expired.
